{"tid":2230250,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–牙膏內為何會添加氟化物？","createTime":"2020-10-04T22:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T14:07:37.000Z","uid":38861,"like":110,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4181f0ec5f07c7546d4db457a797785cf55fa6a7","tid":2230250,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:25:07.000Z","msg":"配合牙膏早晚刷牙能有助預防蛀牙，是眾人皆知的事情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMv5JvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMv5JvR.jpg&h=1daf8de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但你又知唔知為何牙膏普遍會含有氟化物(Fluroide)? 其用意究竟何在呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）牙齒的最外層就係琺瑯質(Enamel)，主要由礦物質hydroxyapatite組成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OR9m1hA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOR9m1hA.jpg&h=bc38aa86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n口腔內的細菌，會從我們進食的食物中攝取糖份，並消化為乳酸，間接導致口水的pH值下降。<br />\n<br />\n當口水pH值低至5.5以下的時候，琺瑯質裡頭的礦物質便會開始被分解，而口腔細菌就會乘虛而入，造成蛀牙。<br />\n<br />\n而牙膏的氟化物能有助抑壓這個酸性分解作用，同時當pH回復正常的時候，氟化物亦能幫忙建構所失去的礦物質。<br />\n<br />\n氟化物還有各種不同的機制預防蛀牙，這裡只列出其中的一項。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）只不過，氟化物牙膏並不是萬能的，原因可從圖中得知。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkGHLKk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkGHLKk.jpg&h=7eb020f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=a5e8f85c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=e1ecb925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。"},{"pid":"223b92d44c6891165651e8c59f65057a43725df2","tid":2230250,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:27:09.000Z","msg":"樓主早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faeea2111ea0ef27096752cd37df506ec29b2860","tid":2230250,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223b92d44c6891165651e8c59f65057a43725df2","tid":2230250,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:27:09.000Z","msg":"樓主早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早晨，不過我準備訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ec62ee88f60d59c1d450f57becfb69d790abbd","tid":2230250,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:31:16.000Z","msg":"氟斑牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f9e5fe0bb539132f1ffbfbea03493b93498c8e","tid":2230250,"uid":284432,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T22:33:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2feec5531e98553d31057d9a08d9bb35ece1e85b","tid":2230250,"uid":165869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c